messages.message: Team, many of the awesome feature functionality and updates need documentation. Guess what? A high-level doc process explains how to make that happen. Check out Stack Overflow for teams: Docs for new, large features (https://stackoverflow.com/c/instabase/questions/31/32#32) for answers to this question. Thanks @Jessica for asking. I owe responses to @Jesika Haria too... ping me if I forgot to create a Jira for your doc request.
cc for those interested, I maintain a list of handy links here in Eng Daily References: https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IB/pages/13729813/Engineering+Daily+References
